{
  "stem": "7832.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then when they-- they shaved my head.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then the next section, they were looking for gold teeth, so they-- we didn't know what they were looking for, but they were telling people to open their mouth.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I had the diamonds in my mouth, so I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I was like watched by that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And it was the last warning, was to put their possessions, because if not, we're going to be punished.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And I had these diamonds in my mouth, so I swallowed them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I was afraid to be caught with them, so I swallowed them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And then we went into another room.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "They told us that we were going to get a shower.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And we did get a shower, a little trickle of a shower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then there was a pile of clothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They shaved our heads.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There was a pile of clothing by that opening, and they ordered everybody to take one piece of clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And so whatever you got, you got.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I got a man's pajama top.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "So being I was so little, it covered me up to here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And so my body was covered.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "A lot of people only got a bottom.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "A lot of people-- it was-- it was-- I looked at the people, and I didn't recognize anybody anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And my cousin's sister-- well, actually, she was my father's cousin, and her sister were in-- in the group with me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I didn't recognize them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "I didn't know which ones they were, because they shaved their heads.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They took their clothing away.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
